First requirement install witty on you system
add ppa repoistory in synaptic manager
ppa:pgquiles/wt
and reload the synaptic package manger and install witty

---------------How to run witty tutorial-------------
1) you have build directory in application. It is empty
cd hello/build
cmake ..
make
~/hello/build/source/hello.wt --http-port 10000 --http-addr 0.0.0.0 --docroot .

localhost:10000
